trans-unit.source: Specifies the behaviors of a link in a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Angir virkem책ten til en kobling i en <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Use the members of this enumeration to set the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkBehavior%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel>.
trans-unit.target: Bruk medlemmene i denne opplistingen til 책 angi verdien for <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkBehavior%2A>egenskapen for <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkBehavior%2A>

trans-unit.source: The link always displays with underlined text.
trans-unit.target: Koblingen viser alltid med understreket tekst.

trans-unit.source: The link displays underlined text only when the mouse is hovered over the link text.
trans-unit.target: Koblingen viser understreket tekst n책r musen holdes over koblingsteksten.

trans-unit.source: The link text is never underlined.
The link can still be distinguished from other text by use of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkColor*> property of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Kan du fortsatt identifiseres koblingen fra andre tekst ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkColor*>for den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel"> </xref> kontroll.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkColor*>

trans-unit.source: The behavior of this setting depends on the options set using the Internet Options dialog box in Control Panel or Internet Explorer.
trans-unit.target: Virkem책ten for denne innstillingen, avhenger av alternativene som angis ved hjelp av dialogboksen Alternativer for Internett i Kontrollpanel eller Internet Explorer.
